Package: dh-gitchangelog
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: foreign
Replaces: dpkg-changelog, genchangelog
Depends:
 git, dh-make, debhelper
Suggests: devscripts
Description: Generate Debian changelogs from git commit messages
 dh-gitchangelog is a tool to generate Debian changelogs from git
 commit messages. It can be used to create a debian/changelog file
 that follows the Debian Policy Manual and the Debian Developer's
 Reference.
 .
 It is designed to be used in conjunction with git, dh-make and
 debhelper, and can be integrated into your workflow to automate
 the process of generating changelogs.
